    <section id="IGNITE+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>IGNITE Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class='graduated'>The Ignite project graduated on 2015-09-18</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>The IGNITE project provides a unified In-Memory Data Fabric providing high-performance,
      distributed in-memory data management software layer between various
      data sources and user applications.</p>
    </section>
